Please follow these steps:
1. Make a Google Drive Folder
2. Upload Media (High Resolution Images and Videos) of all your products you wish to be included in the Swavlamban 2025 Movie.
3. The media can include following:-
(a) Development stages of prototype
(b) Visits by TDAC/ Nodal Officers/ DIO
(c) Conduct of trials / range tests/ lab demos
(d) Displays during seminars/ exhibitions
4. Set the file share option to : "General access:
Anyone on the internet with the link can view"
5. Paste the link below.
